{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 648971, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或者只说书名也行", "timestamp": 1606915805, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 648981, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "霍布斯的利维坦", "timestamp": 1606915916, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 648982, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "乌合之众这种垃圾就别信了", "timestamp": 1606915957, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 648984, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 谢谢啦", "timestamp": 1606915988, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 648986, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: dz不懂，可以细讲讲吗？dz看旁边很多人在读就更了风", "timestamp": 1606916028, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649016, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 看乌合之众的都是乌合之众哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1606916337, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649037, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "乌合之众的很多结论都是作者的感性认识，没有社会调查和理论支持，这本小册子已经被很多人批评了。楼主还是得学习一个啊", "timestamp": 1606916592, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649041, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不要以为各种图书热榜的书就是好书", "timestamp": 1606916626, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649061, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 那有啥比较好的且比较容易读社会学书籍吗？就是有依据而且非文科专业也能看懂的书", "timestamp": 1606916875, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649063, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 哈，有点意思，那Carol有好书推荐吗？dz虽然理工科可也挺喜欢这些的，前提是我看的懂QAQ", "timestamp": 1606916938, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649065, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 同意Carol说的话Hhhh，乌合之众属于那种比较典型的刚一看很牛逼，其实深入思考发现意义比较有限啦。作者经历了法国大革命的混乱，提出了自己感性的认知，是有一定的局限性的。我个人推荐马克思的《路易波拿巴的雾月十八日》hhhh", "timestamp": 1606916942, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649069, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 嗯，我看完就考虑这本，这本容易读吗？感觉马克思的书阅读起来对理工科专业都比较困难", "timestamp": 1606917004, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649072, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "社会性动物蛮好的，社会心理学的书", "timestamp": 1606917077, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649074, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 啊，容易读吗？不会用太多专业名词吧", "timestamp": 1606917115, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649076, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "马克思韦伯，新教伦理与资本主义，儒教与中国。\n刘瑜，民主的细节。", "timestamp": 1606917127, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649077, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 再推荐一本洞穴奇案吧，也是很短的小册子。以及《枪炮细菌与钢铁》（不过这个好像有点烂大街了？）", "timestamp": 1606917135, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649078, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 66666666, 这几本都超级棒！", "timestamp": 1606917173, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649079, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "thanks", "timestamp": 1606917218, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649080, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我推荐错了，上面都是政治哲学的书。\n对于初学者，直接找一本社会心理学课本，厘清基本概念吧", "timestamp": 1606917223, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649084, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: okay👌 👌 ,QAQ", "timestamp": 1606917261, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649092, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "社会心理学目前越来越强调实验手段重复性。比如津巴多的监狱实验已受到不少质疑，看课本要注意版本更新", "timestamp": 1606917371, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649104, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我也是理科生，最开始看雾月十八日是有点困难…………不过看了一些讲大革命历史的B站视频（稚嫩的魔法师做的）再看这本书就好得多了。我室友给我推荐过恩格斯讲科学史和科学范式的书，据说很牛逼不过我还没看过，洞主可以试试23333", "timestamp": 1606917507, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 649175, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 134219, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "心理系博士生强推《这才是心理学：看穿伪心理学的本质》", "timestamp": 1606918817, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 27, "pid": 134219, "reply": 23, "tag": null, "text": "大家知不知道有没有什么和《乌合之众》类似的比较好读的大众心理学书籍啊，求推荐，最好有PDF来源，谢谢啦", "timestamp": 1606915725, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606918816, "url": "", "vote": {}}}